data.value:
AutoMotion by PowerPointLabs simplifies the task of adding the motion path animation to multiple objects on a slide.
1. Duplicate the Slide 2. Move, Resize or Rotate the object you want to animate on the duplicated slide 3. Select the original slide and click on 'Add Animations'
All objects with identical names on the original and duplicated slides are animated. Right-click on an object & click on 'Edit Name' to modify the name of an object.
Want to change the animations added by AutoMotion? Make the required changes on the original or duplicated slides and click on the 'Reload Animations' button after selecting the animated slide added by PPTLabs.
